    <h1>Following endpoints are available</h1>
    <p>
        <li>POST /users - takes a json array and saves it in fileSystem</li>
        <li>GET /users - get the data in the file</li>
		<li>GET /users - get the data in the file based on id</li>
		<li>PUT /users - updates a json element by id. Pass in id and other fields to update as json in request body</li>
        <li>DELETE /users - deletes the data in the file</li>
		<li>DELETE /users/:id - deletes the json element in the file based on id</li>
		<li>DELETE /deleteFile - deletes the json file itself</li>
    </p>
